00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:19,760
like a senior.

253
00:17:21,190 --> 00:17:23,160
Senior.

254
00:17:24,050 --> 00:17:27,060
It's like this, I think

255
00:17:27,060 --> 00:17:29,360
being a little older is great.

256
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:32,590
But Xu Fang...

257
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:39,660
Xu Fang wants to tell you that he doesn't like you and only likes me.

258
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:42,440
It's over!

259
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:46,180
- We just started school and I've already offended a Senior.
- A senior?

260
00:17:46,180 --> 00:17:48,160
Which Senior? What did you do to her?

261
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:51,570
All because of Xu Fang! Senior Jingjing wanted to see him.

262
00:17:51,570 --> 00:17:53,880
He didn't go but made me go.

263
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,970
Later, when Senior was confessing,

264
00:17:55,970 --> 00:18:00,010
he made me tell her that the person he likes is me.

265
00:18:00,010 --> 00:18:02,000
Are you stupid? Did you really say it?

266
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:04,350
Xu Fang was using hands-free.

267
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:05,930
You guys don't even know how adrenaline-filled that situation was.

268
00:18:05,930 --> 00:18:10,420
Good thing I run fast; otherwise, Senior would have killed me.

269
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:15,210
How come when I look at Xu Fang, he looks so cool.

270
00:18:15,210 --> 00:18:18,540
He doesn't seem like someone who would mess with people.

271
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:22,060
When I met Xu Fang, he was 8.

272
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:25,190
That time I already knew that he wasn't a good dog.

273
00:18:25,190 --> 00:18:28,320
Back home, I was the Senior.

274
00:18:28,320 --> 00:18:31,240
He just followed me around like a younger brother.

275
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:34,880
You were the Senior? How could you be Senior like this?

276
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:38,030
You guys don't know! Back then,

277
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:41,990
I climbed trees, harvest bird's nests, picked pomegranates; I could do whatever!

278
00:18:41,990 --> 00:18:44,560
When I climbed trees, he would give me a leg up; when I harvested bird's nests, he would let them free after;

279
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:47,930
I picked pomegranates while he picked them up from the ground.

280
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:53,210
What do you two mean? Don't you believe it?

281
00:18:53,210 --> 00:18:55,310
Seeing Xu Fang now,

282
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:59,720
I completely can't imagine him following you around.

283
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:04,750
I can't imagine it either! How did he grow up to be this wicked?

284
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:07,740
But that's good! He rejected Senior.

285
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:11,830
There should be a lot of people who like him.

286
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:14,470
When did those people become blind?

287
00:19:14,470 --> 00:19:18,680
Speaking of Seniors, do you remember the teacher telling us about a Senior who skipped class?

288
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:20,290
I don't remember.

289
00:19:20,290 --> 00:19:23,030
I remember! Her name is He Liyao.

290
00:19:23,030 --> 00:19:26,530
I remember her! In our school, she placed first in the high school entrance exam for science.

291
00:19:26,530 --> 00:19:29,280
She got into our school but because she's always playing video games,

292
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:32,090
she failed all her classes so she was held back a grade.

293
00:19:32,090 --> 00:19:35,380
She sounds like a legend.

294
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:39,350
If she stayed a grade then she would be in our grade.

295
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:44,280
Maybe this is her bed.

296
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:46,110
How is that possible?

297
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:49,330
Then, who is this empty bed for?

298
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:57,670
What do you come in here for?

299
00:20:57,670 --> 00:20:59,900
Stealing or robbing?

300
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:02,220
Catch him!

301
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:04,640
I couldn't tie him up.

302
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:06,470
Hit him!

303
00:21:06,470 --> 00:21:08,460
Hands off!

304
00:21:09,450 --> 00:21:10,810
It's a girl!

305
00:21:10,810 --> 00:21:13,970
What now? You're disappointed I'm not a handsome guy?

306
00:21:13,970 --> 00:21:17,040
This is my bed!

307
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:20,840
Then why did you come at midnight and dressed like this?

308
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:23,660
My friend called me to help act as an extra.

309
00:21:23,660 --> 00:21:26,990
I came back and you all thought I was a thief. What a luck!

310
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:31,150
What's your name?

311
00:21:31,150 --> 00:21:32,800
He Liyao.

312
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:38,660
You're the one who skipped class and got held back a grade.

313
00:21:38,660 --> 00:21:41,670
It's not that I skipped class.

314
00:21:41,670 --> 00:21:43,960
I missed the exam.

315
00:21:45,190 --> 00:21:46,890
Oh really?

316
00:21:46,890 --> 00:21:50,270
Senior Liyao, that—

317
00:21:52,350 --> 00:21:55,320
Are you okay? I was too nervous before.

318
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:56,850
It's fine.

319
00:21:56,850 --> 00:22:00,390
Let me introduce everyone! I'm Lin Xichi; this is Nie Yue and that is Xin Zidan.

320
00:22:00,390 --> 00:22:02,200
You are Lin Xichi?

321
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,820
What is that expression on your face?

322
00:22:03,820 --> 00:22:06,710
You've made quite a name for yourself, Lin Xichi!

323
00:22:06,710 --> 00:22:10,500
Do you know a senior called Jingjing?

324
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:14,370
She's got her eye on you now.

325
00:22:14,370 --> 00:22:18,280
Good luck!

326
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:19,920
Just kidding!

327
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:22,600
But she really does hate you quite fiercely now.

328
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:26,080
I want to see how you made her become like that.

329
00:22:27,090 --> 00:22:29,230
It's a long story.

330
00:22:29,230 --> 00:22:34,560
There are 5 more years until graduation, how can I survive?

331
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,480
We'll let you get settled in.

332
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:47,970
W-w-we're going to sleep.

333
00:22:54,730 --> 00:22:57,390
We are about to be late. Hurry!

334
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:06,090
Teacher Yan's class, get over here!

335
00:23:14,850 --> 00:23:18,040
Here, Xin Zidan'er!

336
00:23:22,980 --> 00:23:25,630
Why did you come so early today?

337
00:23:25,630 --> 00:23:30,430
I've heard this teacher, Yan Zhibin, is extremely strict.

338
00:23:30,430 --> 00:23:33,160
