339
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:35,060
Look! Everyone's so eager.

340
00:23:35,060 --> 00:23:37,370
Stop talking about it. Isn't it just because there wasn't any other teacher available?

341
00:23:37,370 --> 00:23:38,840
