348
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:07,860
Everyone is here!

349
00:24:12,470 --> 00:24:16,740
Student, pass this around! Everyone signs in for attendance.

350
00:24:17,600 --> 00:24:21,250
- Do you all think that University is a place where you can mess around
- We have class today, hurry over here.

351
00:24:21,250 --> 00:24:23,370
