352
00:24:23,370 --> 00:24:26,150
Skipping class because you feel like it?

353
00:24:27,150 --> 00:24:31,180
If you really think that way, I'll leave you with this phrase.

354
00:24:46,490 --> 00:24:48,860
Deader than dead!

355
00:24:48,860 --> 00:24:51,390
Senior, what does he mean?

356
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:57,960
If you don't study properly, you'll be thoroughly dead.

357
00:24:57,960 --> 00:25:02,300
I just woke up; tell him that I'm in the bathroom, I'll come soon.

358
00:25:02,300 --> 00:25:04,140
Hurry up to come over!

359
00:25:04,140 --> 00:25:07,270
Disguise yourself! I'll be there in a second.

360
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:10,730
- Don't cause trouble for me!
- Think about your wallet!

361
00:25:39,650 --> 00:25:42,140
I will be calling attendance now.

362
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:45,440
Those are called will come up front. No sitting together!

363
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:48,430
This will be the seating arrangement in my class from now on.

364
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:51,220
Tong Ting.

365
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:53,650
- Wan Huanzhong.
- Here.

366
00:25:53,650 --> 00:25:55,910
Wan Liang.

367
00:25:55,910 --> 00:25:57,650
He Liyao.

368
00:25:57,650 --> 00:25:59,300
Here.

369
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:03,720
- Dao Honglin.
- Senior has to retake English class, too?

370
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:06,400
With this teacher... it must be hard not to retake the class.

371
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:08,740
Deng Yue.

