00:26:22,500 --> 00:26:25,140
- Tong Tiangua.
- Here.

379
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:26,740
- Tong Qing.
- Here.

380
00:26:26,740 --> 00:26:29,400
- Zhang Ting.
- Here.

381
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,540
Heng Ho.

382
00:26:31,540 --> 00:26:34,700
- Lin Xichi.
- Here.

383
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:37,760
- Xin Zidan.
- Here.

384
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:40,860
Da Mahou.

385
00:26:40,860 --> 00:26:42,860
- He Nong.
- Here.

386
00:26:42,860 --> 00:26:46,470
