389
00:27:02,430 --> 00:27:05,190
You think that my eyesight is pretty good, isn't it?

390
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:09,710
- What's your name?
- Lin Xichi.

391
00:27:09,710 --> 00:27:12,720
- Where is Xu Fang?
- Pooping!

392
00:27:15,870 --> 00:27:18,470
He's in the bathroom.

393
00:27:18,470 --> 00:27:22,120
You're such a good friend! Why don't you go to the bathroom for him?

394
00:27:28,360 --> 00:27:30,340
You must be Xu Fang.

395
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:32,850
What time is it?

396
00:27:33,600 --> 00:27:36,710
- I had diarrhea.
- Why didn't you wait till after class?

397
00:27:37,970 --> 00:27:40,620
Go ahead and sit down! You'll be marked late.

398
00:27:42,790 --> 00:27:46,490
Impressive! You just started school and you're already letting other students fake attendance for you.

399
00:27:58,970 --> 00:28:03,680
What are you doing? If you didn't want to come, don't come! Don't get me in trouble.

400
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:07,890
I only wanted you to cover for me.

401
00:28:09,190 --> 00:28:11,030
You're not afraid of failing this class?

402
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:15,720
As long as I'm competing for the school, my grades don't matter.

403
00:28:22,690 --> 00:28:27,500
Tonight our department is holding a meeting with old and new students. After dinner, we'll play mafia.

404
00:28:31,090 --> 00:28:34,270
