408
00:28:55,980 --> 00:29:00,280
Werewolves, please open your eyes! Werewolves, please choose who to kill.

409
00:29:03,570 --> 00:29:06,620
Werewolves, close your eyes!

410
00:29:06,620 --> 00:29:09,210
Detective, open your eyes!

411
00:29:09,210 --> 00:29:12,000
Detective, who do you want to check?

412
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:18,650
She's... It's night time, close your eyes.

413
00:29:21,890 --> 00:29:23,590
