414
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:26,180
Chi-Chi, stop talking! You're meant to be dead.

415
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:32,480
Nurse, wake up! You have one antidote, do you want to use it?

416
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:36,140
Nurse, close your eyes. Okay, it's the next morning now.

417
00:29:36,140 --> 00:29:39,540
The game has ended! The werewolves win.

418
00:29:39,540 --> 00:29:41,640
We shouldn't have lost that round.

419
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,980
Lin Xinchi, it's your fault! You kept talking.

420
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:46,850
My fault! I'll take the punishment.

421
00:29:46,850 --> 00:29:49,590
- Truth or dare?
- Choose one.

422
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:51,660
- Truth!
- That's so boring.

423
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:57,730
- Dare, dare, dare!
- Dare!

424
00:29:58,660 --> 00:30:00,440
Let's think about it!

425
00:30:06,810 --> 00:30:12,010
Chi-chi, how about you go to the archery team and ask for someone's WeChat ID?

426
00:30:13,050 --> 00:30:17,320
There are so many people and they are in training; how about—

427
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:22,120
Hurry and go! Hurry up! Go now!

428
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:25,710
Go on!

429
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:45,540
Student, give me your WeChat ID.

430
00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:54,030
Give me your WeChat ID.

431
00:30:58,520 --> 00:31:00,430
Dream on!

432
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:06,640
Forget about it! Let's go.

433
00:31:11,630 --> 00:31:14,540
What's wrong? Are you okay?

434
00:31:14,540 --> 00:31:16,220
I'll go get you some water.

435
00:31:16,220 --> 00:31:19,100
What's up, are you okay?

436
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:25,020
What are you looking at? Just give her your WeChat ID.

437
00:31:25,020 --> 00:31:26,650
None of your business!

438
00:31:29,810 --> 00:31:34,130
- Xu Fang!
- Lin Xichi!

439
00:31:34,130 --> 00:31:36,740
You dog! Are you trying to cause trouble?

440
00:31:36,740 --> 00:31:41,390
Lin Xichi, get off!

441
00:31:41,390 --> 00:31:46,380
- Lin Xichi!
- Let me go!

442
00:31:46,380 --> 00:31:50,020
Lin Xichi, put your legs down!

443
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:52,830
Lin Xichi, were you born in the year of Dog?
(TN: Dog is one of the twelve annual signs in Chinese zodiac)

444
00:31:54,390 --> 00:31:56,100
Lin Xichi, hurry and take me to the school nurse.

445
00:31:56,100 --> 00:31:59,960
- What? Are you trying to fake an injury?
- For real, hurry up!

446
00:32:01,630 --> 00:32:06,450
Let me see! Let's go to School Infirmary.

447
00:32:06,450 --> 00:32:08,620
Let go of me!

448
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:16,400
This fight cured her hiccups.

449
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:20,780
- You don't understand right? Xu Fang pressed Lin Xichi's pressure point.
- Pressure point?

450
00:32:20,780 --> 00:32:24,070
Here! It helps to stop hiccups.

451
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:31,890
My dad's a traditional Chinese medicine practitioner.

452
00:32:33,100 --> 00:32:38,430
Serves you right! How dare you refuse to give your WeChat ID to such a pretty girl like me.

453
00:32:38,430 --> 00:32:41,500
If I didn't know you, the target wouldn't be you.

454
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:45,420
Don't you think that I made you look good in front of your teammates?

455
00:32:47,090 --> 00:32:50,020
Tell me! Besides me, who else would ask for your WeChat ID?

456
00:32:50,020 --> 00:32:52,540
A lot of people!
[Infirmary]

457
00:32:54,410 --> 00:32:58,380
