458
00:32:58,380 --> 00:33:02,850
Even though I'm an aspiring vet and I'm only supposed to treat animals,

459
00:33:02,850 --> 00:33:06,210
I don't mind treating an animal like you.

460
00:33:06,210 --> 00:33:08,820
l'll take my leave now!

461
00:33:08,820 --> 00:33:12,670
- If you don't disinfect it, it'll get infected.
- Do it quickly, then!

462
00:33:14,030 --> 00:33:17,540
How should I charge you for this medical treatment?

463
00:33:20,340 --> 00:33:23,320
How come you're not screaming in pain?

464
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:25,070
This is nothing.

465
00:33:26,140 --> 00:33:29,850
- You're braver than our Fang fang.
- Lin Xichi, you—

466
00:33:29,850 --> 00:33:33,530
No need to thank me! Doctors are meant to save people.

467
00:33:35,210 --> 00:33:38,220
- What happened here?
- Where?

468
00:33:42,330 --> 00:33:47,530
- Did I attack you that aggressively?
- What do you think?

469
00:33:47,530 --> 00:33:50,850
I'm sorry! It was an accident.

470
00:33:52,290 --> 00:33:56,040
If this gets infected, what should we do?

471
00:33:56,040 --> 00:34:00,240
After all, you're my only friend.

472
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:10,930
Chi-chi, why are you so anxious?

473
00:34:10,930 --> 00:34:15,820
Is it because you've realized how dumb you are and you can't live without me?

474
00:34:16,750 --> 00:34:22,060
I was afraid that if something happened to my creditor, I wouldn't be able to afford my meals.

475
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:24,390
S-S-Sorry!

476
00:34:24,390 --> 00:34:29,120
Fang-fang, why don't we stop fighting?

477
00:34:29,120 --> 00:34:32,310
- Dream on!
- Sit down!

478
00:34:33,530 --> 00:34:37,700
- Why?
- I don't want to talk to idiots.

479
00:34:52,780 --> 00:34:57,270
Aren't I obedient? I immediately stopped talking to an idiot.
- You—

480
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:13,600
[Breaking News! Freshman asks campus handsome for WeChat ID, gets rejected and causes a fight that leads to the infirmary!]

481
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:18,650
After being rejected by Xu Fang, she got angry and beat him up so bad that he was sent to the infirmary.

482
00:35:18,650 --> 00:35:23,880
What is this? What is going on?

483
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:28,480
- What are you looking at?
- Chi-chi.

484
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:32,510
Someone took a picture of what happened and sent it to the school newspaper.

485
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:35,690
It said that you asked for Xu Fang's WeChat ID and got rejected.

486
00:35:35,690 --> 00:35:39,170
You got angry and beat him up so bad that he had to go to the infirmary.

487
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:44,910
Can I say that it's not me?

488
00:35:44,910 --> 00:35:48,050
