489
00:35:48,050 --> 00:35:52,870
Also everyone knows you're a new student in the Veterinary Medicine Department and you're known as Big Bro Chi.

490
00:35:55,120 --> 00:35:58,740
- Who said it?
- Don't cry Chi-chi.

491
00:35:58,740 --> 00:36:01,960
Who said it?

492
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:06,800
